the same thing as everyone else.


37
00:01:50.177 --> 00:01:53.680 line:-1 position:50%
This is what we mean
by shared context.


38
00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:57.617 line:-1 position:50%
Shared context also allows us
to communicate effortlessly.


39
00:01:57.617 --> 00:01:59.586 line:-1 position:50%
